title: Extra Innings: The Yanks Are Coming! A lecture from Professor Mick Cox
itunes:author: Mick Cox
description: Contributor(s): Mick Cox | This podcast, we dive into the history of Americans at LSE. As we'll hear from Professor Mick Cox, the LSE has helped shape the United States, and Americans have helped define the LSE since its foundation in 1895.
